      "description": "Multi-analyst FEA ensemble comprising three independently constructed Ansys Mechanical models (FDA analyst, Ansys consulting, DePuy Synthes analyst) of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct per ASTM F1717 fixture geometry. Hexahedral-dominant mesh; Ti-6Al-4V linear-elastic constitutive model; frictional contact at screw-block interface.",
      "uofa:isFoundationalEvidence": true
    }
